  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Introduction"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page provides an overview for the establishing and maintaining the traceability for FuSa artifacts delivered from CART, with CN CONV project requirements (Ex: Zeeker)"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Artifacts from CART"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The following is the delivery plan committed from CART team,"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "„FRS (SWRS) - CART DOORS",
        "„SWCDD – storage TBD for ConvBase",
        "„Code",
        "„UT",
        "„QAC",
        "„FIT",
        "Inspection Reviews for ConvBase components"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Traceability process flow for requirements"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "FSHLR/SysRS/TSR are part of DOORS Hi Server in project area (Ex: Zeeker)",
        "Using xChange tool, copy of the SWRS/HLR (for SMs) from CART shall be placed in CN CONV PF",
        "Further linking from the copy here, shall be possible (Ex: to TSR, SWCDD etc)",
        "Project config shall be updated with new sub module in DOORS project area(Zeeker) and linked",
        "RQM/Test specification document link shall be added"
      ]
    },
